    "author_association": "NONE",
    "body": "Is this unexpected?  I know that I would personally be very surprised to find string members initialized to empty strings.  I would expect class members to have default values as they do in other .NET languages.  Coercing null to empty string is already a confusing foot gun in other contexts, I wouldn’t want to see it extended to classes. ",
