    "body": "Point taken, and I agree that it’s a bit inconsistent.  I guess I’m just voicing a preference for aligning with C# in this context.  As you note, in many ways, it already is.\r\n\r\nNo one has ever had to learn about [NullString]::Value and been happy about it.  I know it’s too late for that, but I’d hate to have it show up more than it already has to. ",
